name: United Kingdom Geography - Regions Counties and Cities
desc:
Additional Documentation and Feedback The deck will help you to learn:
  • 12 top level regions (e.g. Scotland, East of England...)
  • 32 Scottish Council Areas and 64 Ceremonial Counties for England, Wales, and Northern Ireland
  • 69 Official Cities
  • 15 assorted seas, channels, estuaries, straits and oceans
Deck Features
  • The deck is light-weight (~3MB, despite containing ~500 unique images)
  • All images are Scalable Vector Graphics and therefore scale gracefully to any screen size without distortion
  • Colours are distribued across maps to encourage colour-based memory retention
  • CSS and JS is used to generate and animate images
This deck is maintained on GitHub. Found a bug? Interested in adding new cards or new features? Raise an issue or check out the project documentation on Github.
